<br>
Mindbogglingly waste of time and energy imho.<br>
<br>
We use the simpliest (sp?) system we could imagine: all get 3 dkp/hour of raiding (sometimes on shit encounters... Rathe .. Xeg .. there is a 5-10 dkp bonus) and on all items dropped there is a quick auction, bids start on 1.<br>
<br>
Pros: Super simple logging: just have a bot doing &quot;/who all GUILD&quot; every hour on the hour. No special rules for anything: highest bidder wins. period.<br>
<br>
Cons: If peeps raise by 1 auction can drag on (use a separate chat channel). Peeps can hoard points to buy cheaper later but so what, let em. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=151334">Pling, Maestro of AB</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <br><font color=#330000>- </font><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/btheconcerthall>The Concert Hall - Message Boards</a><font color=#330000> - </font><a href=http://p201.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallbackstage>Backstage</a><font color=#330000> - </font><br><br><br><br>Powered By <a href=http://www.ezboard.com/>ezboard®</a> Ver. 7.31p<br>Copyright ©1999-2003 ezboard, Inc.</center></body></html>  